## Основные Principles
- **Analytical comme.ts**: Add comme.ts explaining logic and architectural decisions for AI understanding
- **Context explanations**: Explain "why", not just "what" the code does
- **Architectural comme.ts**: Document component relationships and data flows
- **Business logic**: Explain complex business logic and decisions made
- **TODO comme.ts**: Leave TODO with explanation of planned improveme.ts

